dct_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines, Passaic River, N.J., Montclair and Greenwood Lake R.R. Bridge to Wall St., Bridge, Passaic
dct_description_sm: Nautical chart showing the pierhead and bulkhead lines along the Passaic River, New Jersey
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Map is in poor condition around edges, some creases cause information to be obscured.
Date is inferred from the U.S.E.D. survey date of 1927
